---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Soumyo Dey">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This Privacy Policy explains how this website collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit ace139.github.io.
        I value your privacy and am committed to being transparent about my data practices.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Information Collection</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        When you visit this website, certain information may be automatically collected:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li>Usage data (pages visited, time spent on pages, referring websites)</li>
        <li>Device information (browser type, operating system, screen resolution)</li>
        <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This information is collected using privacy-focused analytics tools that respect your privacy.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This website uses cookies for the following purposes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> These are necessary for the website to function properly (e.g., remembering your dark/light mode preference).</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> These help understand how visitors interact with the website, enabling improvements to the user experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Third-party cookies:</strong> Some content from external services (like embedded social media posts) may set their own cookies.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">
        You can control cookies through your browser settings or by using the cookie consent banner on this website.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Analytics</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This website uses Plausible Analytics, a privacy-focused analytics service that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li>Does not use cookies for tracking visitors</li>
        <li>Does not collect personal information</li>
        <li>Does not track visitors across devices or websites</li>
        <li>Is fully compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and other privacy regulations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This website may include content from third-party services such as:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li>Social media embeds (Twitter/X)</li>
        <li>Newsletter subscription services (Substack)</li>
        <li>Font providers</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">
        These services may collect data about you according to their own privacy policies, which are outside of my control.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This website implements security measures to protect your information, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
        <li>Regular security updates</li>
        <li>Minimal data collection practices</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
        <li>Right to access information collected about you</li>
        <li>Right to request deletion of your information</li>
        <li>Right to opt-out of certain data collection</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in data practices or legal requirements.
        Significant changes will be communicated through the website.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact me through the contact information provided on this website.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-8">
      Last updated: May 2024
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
